title: The Scary Truth of New Age Practices with Natalies Outlet
description:
Law of attraction, manifestation, tarot cards, omens, energy, sage, mediums, and more... These are all part of the New Age practice.  Jeanine wants to share with you all the dangers of these things. This may be controversial, but it's necessary. Listen to Natalie's story today and how she left new age practices for God's truth! Hope you enjoy and listen to this with an open mind. Thanks for listening!
